@startuml
title Hình 5.12 - Kết quả k6 catalog, checkout và flash-sale spike

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #475569
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam ComponentBorderColor #475569
skinparam ComponentBackgroundColor #E0F2FE
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #475569
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #DCFCE7

left to right direction

actor "k6 load generator\nlocal machine" as K6
component "AWS EC2\nproduction-like stack" as Stack #EEF2FF
component "API Gateway" as Gateway #DCFCE7
database ".test/results\nraw artifacts" as Results #DCFCE7

rectangle "Catalog soak\n34m03s\n200 VU\n220,956 requests\np95 61.68 ms\nerror 0.00%" as Catalog #DBEAFE
rectangle "Checkout stress\n7m00s\n50 VU\n13,734 requests\np95 160.92 ms\nerror 0.00%" as Checkout #ECFDF5
rectangle "Flash-sale spike\n1m30s\n500 VU\n78,448 requests\n100/100 slots\n0 duplicate buyer\np95 overall 1.04 s" as Flash #FEF3C7

K6 --> Catalog
K6 --> Checkout
K6 --> Flash

Catalog --> Gateway : GET catalog/search
Checkout --> Gateway : create order flow
Flash --> Gateway : flash-sale purchase
Gateway --> Stack : route to services

Catalog --> Results : json/txt output
Checkout --> Results : json/txt output
Flash --> Results : json/txt output

note bottom
  Mục tiêu của hình là tổng hợp bằng chứng hiệu năng.
  Khi có ảnh chụp terminal k6 thật, có thể thay hình này bằng screenshot.
end note

@enduml
